      },
      "widgets_values": [
        "Did you know that there is a version of you that already started? They uploaded their first video a few months ago. And it was a disaster. It was the worst one yet. The audio cut out more than twice, they talked too fast, and the lighting made them look bad. But then, they uploaded the next one. And another one. And another one...",
        "Hello! I am testing this new digital voice. Every small detail counts when we speak. I want my voice to sound warm, clear, and completely natural. Let's see how well this works. Did you know... that there is a version of you... that already started? They uploaded their first video, just a few months ago. And, honestly... it was a complete disaster. But then... they kept going. One video, at a time. And that... is how you truly build something great.",
